#

Herbed Cream Cheese and Tomato Toast

15 min
$4.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

QuickEasyAppetizer

Description

Deliciously creamy and savory with a hint of freshness from the herbs, this toast is perfect for a quick snack or light meal.

Ingredients

  • sourdough bread: 2 slices
  • cream cheese: 4 tablespoons
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • fresh basil leaves: 1/4 cup
  • fresh chives: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
